</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><span class="mbox-text-span">This article <b>may be too <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/technical#Adjective" class="extiw" title="wikt:technical">technical</a> for most readers to understand</b>. <span class="hide-when-compact">Please help <a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Socialism&action=edit.php.html">improve</a> this article to <a href="Wikipedia_Make_technical_articles_understandable" title="Wikipedia:Make technical articles understandable">make it understandable to non-experts</a>, without removing the technical details. The <a href="Talk_Socialism" title="Talk:Socialism">talk page</a> may contain suggestions.</span> <small><i>(November 2012)</i></small> </span></td>
