<li id="cite_note-24"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.rdwolff.com/sites/default/files/attachment/4/State%20Capitalism%20versus%20Communism%20CS%202008.pdf">"State Capitalism versus Communism: What happened in the USSR and PRC?"</a> (PDF)<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.rdwolff.com/sites/default/files/attachment/4/State%20Capitalism%20versus%20Communism%20CS%202008.pdf">http://www.rdwolff.com/sites/default/files/attachment/4/State%20Capitalism%20versus%20Communism%20CS%202008.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 19 September 2012</span>.</span></span></li>
