<li id="cite_note-35"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-35">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book"><a href="Socialist_Party_of_Great_Britain" title="Socialist Party of Great Britain">Socialist Party of Great Britain</a> (1985) (PDF). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldsocialism.org/spgb/pdf/ms.pdf"><i>The Strike Weapon: Lessons of the Miners' Strike</i></a>. London: Socialist Party of Great Britain<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.worldsocialism.org/spgb/pdf/ms.pdf">http://www.worldsocialism.org/spgb/pdf/ms.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 28 April 2007</span>.</span></span></li>
