<li id="cite_note-ReferenceA-48"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-ReferenceA_48-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ReferenceA_48-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Karl Marx, Preface to A Contribution to the Critique of Political Economy, 1859</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-ComparingEconomic-49"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-ComparingEconomic_49-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i>Comparing Economic Systems in the Twenty-First Century</i>, 2003, by Gregory and Stuart. P.62, <i>Marx's Theory of Change</i>. <a href="Special_BookSources/0618261818" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-618-26181-8</a>.</span></li>
