<li id="cite_note-fsmitha.com-86"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-fsmitha.com_86-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-fsmitha.com_86-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-fsmitha.com_86-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.fsmitha.com/h3/h44-ph.html">"Adam Smith"</a>. Fsmitha.com<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.fsmitha.com/h3/h44-ph.html">http://www.fsmitha.com/h3/h44-ph.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2 June 2010</span>.</span></span></li>
