<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="background:#e54a46; color:white;;;">Concepts</th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd hlist">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li><a href="Economic_planning" title="Economic planning">Economic planning</a></li>
<li><a href="Free_association_(communism_and_anarchism)" title="Free association (communism and anarchism)">Free association</a></li>
